{"tid":1004784,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"新手砌機求指教!","createTime":"2019-02-01T16:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T03:56:49.000Z","uid":29213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c785649d5d271caf8fb550d546c6d9bbee701ba7","tid":1004784,"uid":29213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T16:52:25.000Z","msg":"咁多位巴打<br />\n小弟依家用緊既電腦都用左有一段長時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見岩岩公司出左花紅有小小錢淨所以想upgrade下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家既spec係咁既<br />\nCPU :I5-2400<br />\nMotherboard: Gigabyte Z68MA-D2H-B3<br />\ndisplay card: GTX 960<br />\nRam : 2x  8GB DDR3 1866<br />\n最主要想換左CPU同motherboard<br />\nCPU諗住會換i5-8400(約1500hkd)<br />\nmotherboard有人介紹 asus既 B360 H-gaming((約700hkd)<br />\n因為我就唔太用電腦打機，就算打都唔要求開到好盡。所以唔洗去到好靚<br />\n唔知各位巴打有冇咩其他推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但睇返塊motherboard好似唔support 我依家用緊既ram<br />\n咁我係咪連ram都要換埋???<br />\n如果係既話又換邊一隻ram好<br />\n另外依家已經有隻全新240gb既ssd係手<br />\n想再買隻1 TB既HHD，想睇下有咩牌子信得過<br />\n大約budget只有4000左右，唔知夠唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25a7b4c76d0f2339dd034d9a4fc636a9b30211a","tid":1004784,"uid":52424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T17:07:02.000Z","msg":"換CPU MB 要換埋ram"},{"pid":"6b6d26542314755944ecfe83cd70b64d6f9a017a","tid":1004784,"uid":29213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c25a7b4c76d0f2339dd034d9a4fc636a9b30211a","tid":1004784,"uid":52424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20